Description: Computes heteroskedasticity-consistent covariance matrix
    estimators for linear regression models, including the classical HC
    family and the HCbeta estimator. The package provides normal Wald tests,
    confidence intervals, diagnostics, and polished S3 output for applied
    inference.
URL: https://prdm0.github.io/hcinfer, https://github.com/prdm0/hcinfer
